#### [MODIFY] [coupon.controller.ts](file:///e:/MY-PROJECTS/2m%20tech/server/src/controllers/coupon.controller.ts)

**#15 — Coupon discount can exceed subtotal**

In [order.controller.ts](file:///e:/MY-PROJECTS/2m%20tech/server/src/controllers/order.controller.ts) `newOrder`, cap the discount:

```diff
 computedDiscount = coupon.amount;
+// Cap discount so order never goes negative
+computedDiscount = Math.min(computedDiscount, computedSubTotal);
```

