#### [MODIFY] [settings.controller.ts](file:///e:/MY-PROJECTS/2m%20tech/server/src/controllers/settings.controller.ts)

**#10 — Cannot clear fields**

`phone || settings.phone` prevents setting a field to empty string `''`. Fix by checking for `undefined`:

```diff
-settings.companyName = companyName || settings.companyName;
+settings.companyName = companyName !== undefined ? companyName : settings.companyName;
```

Apply to all fields.

---

#### [MODIFY] [settings.model.ts](file:///e:/MY-PROJECTS/2m%20tech/server/src/models/settings.model.ts)

**#11 — `via.placeholder.com` default logo URL**

Replace with a local placeholder path or empty string.

---

#### [MODIFY] [index.ts](file:///e:/MY-PROJECTS/2m%20tech/server/src/index.ts)

**#16 — Error middleware ordering**

```diff
-app.use((err: any, req: Request, res: Response, next: NextFunction) => { ... });
-app.use(apiErrorMiddleware);
+app.use(apiErrorMiddleware);
+app.use((err: any, req: Request, res: Response, next: NextFunction) => { ... });
```

The [apiErrorMiddleware](file:///e:/MY-PROJECTS/2m%20tech/server/src/utils/ApiError.ts#10-27) handles structured [ApiError](file:///e:/MY-PROJECTS/2m%20tech/server/src/utils/ApiError.ts#3-9) instances first. The global catch-all handles everything else.

**#18 — Unused Firebase Firestore init**

```diff
-try {
-  firebaseApp.firestore();
-} catch (error) {
-  console.error('Firebase initialization error:', error);
-}
```

Remove this block — the app uses Firebase Auth only, not Firestore.

