#### [MODIFY] [upload.middleware.ts](file:///e:/MY-PROJECTS/2m%20tech/server/src/middleware/upload.middleware.ts)

**#13 — No file-type restriction**

This middleware appears unused (the Cloudinary upload middleware is used instead), but if it's kept, add [fileFilter](file:///e:/MY-PROJECTS/2m%20tech/server/src/utils/cloudinary.ts#31-39):

```diff
 const upload = multer({
     storage: storage,
+    fileFilter: (req, file, cb) => {
+        if (file.mimetype.startsWith('image/')) {
+            cb(null, true);
+        } else {
+            cb(new Error('Only image files are allowed'));
+        }
+    },
+    limits: { fileSize: 10 * 1024 * 1024 }
 });
```

